In [2]:
def getDownload(url, param = None, retries = 3):
    resp = None
    try:
        resp = requests.get(url, params = param, headers = header)
        resp.raise_for_status()
    except requests.exceptions.HTTPError as e:
        if 500 <= resp.status_code < 600 and retries > 0:
            print('Retries : {0}'.format(retries))
            return getDownload(url, param, retries -1)
        else:
            print(resp.status_code)
            print(resp.reason)
            print(resp.request.headers)
            
    return resp

Daum 검색결과 param = 파이썬 (사이트)¶

In [21]:
url = 'https://search.daum.net/search?w=tot&DA=YZR&t__nil_searchbox=btn&sug=&sugo=&q=%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%B4%EC%8D%AC'
# url = 'https://search.daum.net/search'
# param = {'q':'파이썬} # param 사용 하셔도 됩니다.
# html = getDownload(url,param)
html = getDownload(url)
dom = BeautifulSoup(html.text, 'lxml')

for tag in dom.find('',{'disp-attr':'IVR'}).find_all('',{'class':'f_link_b'}):
    print(tag.text)
    print(tag['href'])
